{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Atgreeſeetees mannas Mei-\ntab/ eita nohſt/ jo es efmu dauds\nwezza/ ka es buhtu man Wihrnu\nnehnuſt. Kad es ta tazzitu: man\nirr wehl Zerribas/ un jepſchu man\narrtoſan ſchinni Naſti weens\nWihrs taptu/ un Dehluſ djeim-\ndetu/"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ar tad juhs gaiditat/ ka-\nmeir winni uſaugtu? woj juhs\nkawetatees Wihrnu ne xemt? ne\nta mannas Meitas/ manirr juh-\nfu wairak ſchehl/ ne ka junis pa-\nſchabm/ jo ta KUNGA Rohka irr\nprett man iſſteeputſees."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad pazehſte tahs fawn\nBalesni/ un raudaja atkaſ/ un\nArpa ſchupſtija fawn Mahtizi/\nbet Rutte palikke pee winnas."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija ta: Reds/ ta-\ntwa Mahrſcha irr atgreeſufees pee\nfaweem Landim/ un pee fatweem\nDeeweem/ atgreeſees ir tu tawai\nMahrſchai pakkat."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Rutte fazzija : Ne-\nrunna man pretti/ ka man buhs\nno tewis atkahpt/ un atgreeſtees\nno tewis atpakat/ jo kurp tu eefi/\neefhu es lihdsi/ un kur tu pee-\nmahjofi/ tur peemahjofchu es lih-\ndsi ar tew/ tawi Landisirr man-\nni Landis/ un taws Deews irr\nnians Deews."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kur tu nomirſi/ tur no-\nmirſhu es/ un tur gribbu es ap-\nrakta tapt/lai tas KUNGS man\nta darra/ un ta peeleeſ/ ja ue ta\nNahwe ween mann un tewi\nſchkire,"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu winna redſeja/ ka"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad gahje tee abbee/\nmeir tee nahze us Betlemi/\nkad winna us Betlemi nahze/t\nzehlahs wiſs Pilſtahts pahr tee-\nun tee fazzija : Irrag tchi ta Na-\nemja?"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet winna fazzija\ntahn: ne nofauzeet mann p\nNaëmju/fauzeet mann par Ma-\nrn/ jo tas Wiſſuwarrenajs\nman leelu Sirde Ruhtnu-\nveefuhtijs."
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Piina niſgahju es/\ntukſchu irr man tas KUNG\nlizzis atgreestees/ kapehz faukſ-\njuhs mann Naëmja/ fur tome-\ntas KUNGS prett mann\nLeezibu devis/ un tas Wiſſuwo-\nrenajs irr mann apbehdtuajs."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta atgreeſahs Naëmja\nRutte ta Moabiteru Geewa wi-\nnas Weddele ar winnu/ atgre-\ndamees no Moaba/ un tahs na-\nze us Betlemi ap to Meesc-\nPtautchanas Laiku."
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
